{"title":"Salsa Cycles Crank Up the Heat with Prototype eMTB & Gravel eBikes!","link":"https://bikerumor.com/salsa-cycles-prototype-emtb-gravel-ebikes/","date":1683049794000,"content":"<p>From the looks of things at Sea Otter, Salsa Cycles is the next brand to venture into the world of eBikes. Not-so-hidden in their booth were two new bikes – the Confluence gravel prototype, and a prototype MTB called the Notch. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike4-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Salsa Notch eMTB prototype\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike4-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike4-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike4-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike4-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike4-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike4.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike1-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Salsa Notch eMTB prototype\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike1-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike1-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike1-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike1-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike1.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike3-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Salsa Notch eMTB prototype\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike3-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike3-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike3-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike3-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike3-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike3.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike2-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Salsa Notch eMTB prototype split pivot\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike2-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike2-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike2-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike2-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike2.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Clearly labeled as a prototype, the Notch is the more secretive of the two bikes. Salsa wouldn’t give us any details other than the fact that they’re working on an e-MTB, and what we can see – like the Split Pivot suspension design. Equipped with a Bosch motor and battery system, the Notch prototype had 29 x 2.6″ Teravail Kessel tires front and rear and a Rockshox ZEB suspension fork that looked to be in the realm of 160-170mm of travel. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Confluence Gravel Prototype</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike10.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike10-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Salsa Cycles confluence gravel ebike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike10-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike10-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike10-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike10-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike10-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike10-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike10.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>More is known about the Confluence gravel bike, even though it is still a prototype – the color and spec above are not production, but close. Built with a MAHLE SmartBike X35 system, the bike is a Class 1 with a 20mph top assisted speed, with 40 Nm of torque and a 250 Wh battery in the downtube. Like other MAHLE bikes, it will be compatible with their 208 Wh range extender to increase total battery to 458 Wh. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike9.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike9-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Salsa Cycles confluence gravel ebike button\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike9-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike9-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike9-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike9-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike9-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike9-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike9.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike8.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike8-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Salsa Cycles confluence gravel ebike dropper\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike8-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike8-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike8-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike8-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike8-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike8-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike8.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike7.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike7-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Salsa Cycles confluence gravel ebike drivetrain\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike7-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike7-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike7-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike7-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike7-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike7-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike7.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike5.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike5-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Salsa Cycles confluence gravel ebike flat bar\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike5-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike5-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike5-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike5-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike5-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Salsa-eBike-prototype-Notch-Confluence-gravel-bike5.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Designed around a 6061-T6 aluminum frame, the Confluence will be offered in six frame sizes for dropbar builds, and five frame sizes for flat bar builds. The frames will include a Confluence-specific full carbon gravel fork with a 12x100mm thru axle, and the bikes will have a 700c x 50mm tire clearance. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Other frame details include internal droper post compatibility, 68mm threaded bottom brackets, rack and fender mounts, and cargo mounts. Complete bikes will start around $2,499 with availability TBD. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.salsacycles.com\" target=\"_blank\">salsacycles.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/salsa-cycles-prototype-emtb-gravel-ebikes/\">Salsa Cycles Crank Up the Heat with Prototype eMTB &amp; Gravel eBikes!</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Zach Overholt","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"d18b7365614c6d6a7b764101246bbf34ad06336f309e055d8da3b8da7057addd","category":"Cycling"}